         We also welcome you to come see your adopted book in person â€“ just be in touch with Christa Bernardo to schedule a time.  To learn more about our Adopt-A-Book program or supporting other areas of the UC Libraries, contact Christa Bernardo at (513) 556-0055 or <a href="mailto:christa.bernardo@uc.edu">christa.bernardo@uc.edu</a>.
         Thank you for generosity and support of the UC Libraries. <br>
      </p>
   </div>
</div>
